hopobject.body: Is it convenient to talk at the moment? barakat-pharma.com My test drive of the MotoMaker site was simple and fun. The best part is what happens after you order: Motorola will build the phone in Ft. Worth, TX and deliver it to you in four days or less. Non-AT&T customers can choose from black or white models. And AT&T customers that can’t wait for a Moto X can take a black or white model home as a loaner until their custom Moto X arrives.
